#Text=David
#Text=McIntosh ( Gladiators )
#Text=This article is about the British actor .
#Text=For others with similar names , see David McIntosh .
#Text=David McIntosh ( born 10 December 1985 ) is a British ex-military and security operative who became a television personality , actor , and fitness model .
#Text=A former Royal Marines commando , he was a Gladiator on the Sky 1 TV series Gladiators , under the name Tornado . [ 1 ]
#Text=In 2014 , he participated in Celebrity Big Brother 14 . [ 2 ]
#Text=Career
#Text=Born to a British mother and Jamaican father , McIntosh grew up in Platt Bridge , near Wigan .
#Text=He went to Holy Family Primary School in Platt Bridge and then St Edmund Arrowsmith high school in Ashton in Makerfield .
#Text=After school , McIntosh became a Royal Marines Commando , serving in Northern Ireland , Somalia , the Persian Gulf , and Afghanistan . [ 3 ]
#Text=Upon leaving the Marines , McIntosh took on the role of Gladiator " Tornado " on the Sky 1 show Gladiators . [ 4 ]
#Text=Following Gladiators , McIntosh worked in security . [ 5 ]

#Text=In late 2013 , McIntosh worked in security transportation on a badger culling operation , and after crashing a van loaded with dead badgers into a bus stop he received a traffic violation resulting in a court fine . [ 6 ]
#Text=McIntosh was also found guilty of driving for eight years with a license that had been revoked for a previous traffic violation . [ 7 ]
#Text=In 2014 , McIntosh appeared in fitness magazine " Muscle & Fitness " , the Jennifer Hudson music video " Walk It Out " , and the Nicki Minaj music video " Anaconda " .

column1: #Text=In August 2014 , McIntosh entered the Celebrity Big Brother house [ 8 ] for a reported fee of £200,000 . [ 9 ]
#Text=McIntosh was the first to be evicted from the house . [ 10 ]
#Text=In 2016 McIntosh sparked outrage by making an FB post in which he compared Orthodox Jewish women appearance without wigs to " witches " which has been labeled anti-semitic . [ 11 ]
#Text=In 2017 , David Mcintosh joined the cast of " Famously Single 2 " which is a celebrity dating show on the E ! channel .
#Text=Later that year he joined the ITV2 Ancient Rome -themed reality television series Bromans .
#Text=He played Doctore , mentoring the contestants during physical challenges . [ 12 ]
#Text=Personal life
#Text=McIntosh has been reported to date celebrities including Gina Rodriguez , Danielle Lloyd , Sara Jones , [ 13 ]
#Text=Chantelle Houghton , [ 14 ]
#Text=Rachel Christie , Sarah Harper , [ 15 ]
#Text=Chanelle Hayes , Metisha Schaefer , Kelly Brook , Aisleyne Horgan-Wallace , and Juliet Bakos .
#Text=McIntosh claimed to have not dated Rodriguez , [ 16 ] and not know Houghton .
#Text=In 2011
#Text=McIntosh became a father with Christie to their son Logan Phoenix McIntosh . [ 17 ]
#Text=Following a breakdown in their relationship , Christie secured a non-molestation order against McIntosh . [ 18 ]
#Text=In March 2014 McIntosh and Brook announced their engagement , split up in September 2014 , [ 19 ] reconciled in October 2014 , and split up permanently in November 2014 .

#Text=Following the split , McIntosh demanded that Brook compensate him for gifts he had given during the relationship , however Brook declined , and described her relationship with McIntosh as " toxic " .
#Text=In July 2015 it was reported that McIntosh bullied Brook during their relationship , a charge that McIntosh denied . [ 20 ]
